{
  "stem": "1132.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We had a protection paper from the Swiss government, which I have and I hope you'll take a picture of.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we also had the Papal protection paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I don't have it here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "My sister has that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I clearly remember the importance of these papers, because they really protected us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Now, as far as going back chronologically what has happened, as the year went on, '44, everyone had to wear the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we had a curfew by which we had to be back in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "The door got locked and you were not allowed to go out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I remember raids as the Arrowheads came in and started taking able-bodied woman, and teenagers, and men away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I clearly remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Somehow or other we survived it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I don't know how, but every time as more and more people were taken away and rounded up to be taken to the trains and to the concentration camps, we remained.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Again, I give a lot of credit to my parents.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I simply don't know how they managed, but they did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Now I have very vivid recollection of a ver-- a winter night-- winter afternoon, to begin with.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "My father was away and he sent word to my mother, who happened to be sick at the time, that he wanted us to leave this building where we have been for the last several months because he knew that the next roundup will include us as well, and there was no way we are going to be escaping that.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what he said was we should find some protect-- protection, some way how we can leave this building.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he left an address where he wanted us to go to.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
